Package: tidycomp
Title: Tidyverse-Style Functions for Statistical Comparisons and Diagnostics
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Dauber", , "daniel.dauber.io@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4324-4796"))
Description: Provides a consistent, tidyverse-friendly interface for statistical group 
    comparisons and diagnostic checks. Includes wrappers for common tests 
    (parametric, non-parametric, and robust), automatic effect size computation 
    via the 'effectsize' package, and data diagnostics for outliers, missing data, 
    and potential bias sources. Designed to integrate seamlessly with the 'tidymodels' 
    ecosystem and follow tidyverse style conventions.
